page.title: 17AUCHNAGATT COUNTRYSIDE.
page.content: Around Auchnagatt most of our countryside is taken up by farmland. There are a lot of beef and dairy cattle arond the area.Trees and woodland occupy a small portion of the high ground in our block.All over the place around woodland,roads and tracks you will find hogweed and cow parsly covering the ground.Most wild flowers that can be found around Auchnagatt are: {Buttercups,daisies,forget-me-nots, {,vetch,white clover and speedwell. {Wildlife: Foxes,rabbits,hares,frogs,bats,mice and moles occupy most of wildlife around and in Auchnagatt.Insects. Spiders, Blue Bottles, Flys, Butter Fly, Bees, Wasps, and Beetles.The main thing about the countryside in our block is that there are trees and wildlife.
